(255, '_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e', '<h4>Самые популярные</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/contact-form-plugin/''>Contact Form</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=contact-form-plugin&amp;_wpnonce=f6a88042cb&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Contact Form''>Установить</a>)</span>\n<p>Add Contact Form to your WordPress website.</p>\n<h4>Самые свежие</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/triagis-security-evaluation/''>Triagis Security Evaluation</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=triagis-security-evaluation&amp;_wpnonce=e0fa4b15f6&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Triagis Security Evaluation''>Установить</a>)</span>\n<p>Triagis Security Evaluation is a simple lite-weight plugin to analyze your current Wordpress installation and server config for common security flaws.</p>\n', 'no');
